    "question": "Basic steps to give Contributor and Reader role",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>Basic steps to give Contributor and Reader role</strong></h3>\n  <p>•\tSign in to Azure Portal.</p>\n  <p>•\tGo to the Subscription/Resource Group/Resource.</p>\n  <p>•\tSelect Access Control (IAM).</p>\n  <p>•\tClick Add > Add Role Assignment.</p>\n  <p>•\tSelect the role:</p>\n  <p>•\tContributor</p>\n  <p>•\tReader</p>\n  <p>•\tSelect the User, Group, or Service Principal.</p>\n  <p>•\tClick Review + Assign.</p>\n</div>",
