    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>How do you handle zero-downtime deployment?</strong></h3>\n  <p>“We use deployment strategies like:</p>\n  <p>Blue-Green Deployment</p>\n  <p>•\tTwo environments:</p>\n  <p>•\tBlue (current)</p>\n  <p>•\tGreen (new)</p>\n  <p>•\tTraffic switches after validation</p>\n  <p>Rolling Updates</p>\n  <p>•\tGradual pod replacement</p>\n  <p>•\tNo complete downtime</p>\n  <p>We also:</p>\n  <p>•\tMonitor application health</p>\n  <p>•\tUse load balancers</p>\n  <p>•\tValidate readiness probes</p>\n  <p>One-line Answer:</p>\n  <p>I use rolling updates and blue-green deployments for zero downtime.”</p>\n</div>",
