    "question": "Agent not picking job – why?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>Agent not picking job – why?</strong></h3>\n  <p>“Possible reasons:</p>\n  <p>•\tAgent offline</p>\n  <p>•\tCapability mismatch</p>\n  <p>•\tIncorrect pool configuration</p>\n  <p>•\tPermission issue</p>\n  <p>Troubleshooting:</p>\n  <p>•\tCheck agent service status</p>\n  <p>•\tValidate pool assignment</p>\n  <p>•\tVerify required capabilities</p>\n  <p>One-line Answer:</p>\n  <p>I verify agent health, capabilities, and pool configuration.”</p>\n  <p>Pipeline triggered but not running</p>\n  <p>“Common reasons:</p>\n  <p>•\tTrigger misconfiguration</p>\n  <p>•\tWrong branch filters</p>\n  <p>•\tYAML syntax issue</p>\n  <p>•\tDisabled pipeline</p>\n  <p>I check:</p>\n  <p>•\ttrigger section</p>\n  <p>•\tbranch filters</p>\n  <p>•\tpipeline logs</p>\n  <p>•\tYAML validation</p>\n  <p>One-line Answer:</p>\n  <p>I verify triggers, branch filters, and YAML syntax.”</p>\n  <p>Permission denied error</p>\n  <p>“This usually happens because of:</p>\n  <p>•\tRBAC issue</p>\n  <p>•\tInvalid service connection</p>\n  <p>•\tMissing access rights</p>\n  <p>Steps:</p>\n  <p>•\tValidate service connection</p>\n  <p>•\tCheck Azure IAM roles</p>\n  <p>•\tVerify Kubernetes RBAC</p>\n  <p>•\tEnsure resource permissions</p>\n  <p>One-line Answer:</p>\n  <p>I resolve permission errors by validating RBAC and service connection access.”</p>\n</div>",
