    "question": "What is VPN Gateway?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>What is VPN Gateway?</strong></h3>\n  <p>“Azure VPN Gateway securely connects:</p>\n  <p>•\tOn-premises datacenter</p>\n  <p>•\tRemote users</p>\n  <p>•\tAzure VNets</p>\n  <p>Types:</p>\n  <p>•\tSite-to-Site VPN</p>\n  <p>•\tPoint-to-Site VPN</p>\n  <p>Traffic is encrypted over internet.</p>\n  <p>One-line Answer:</p>\n  <p>VPN Gateway securely connects on-premises environments to Azure.”</p>\n</div>",
