    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>☁️ <strong>What is Azure Scale Set?</strong></h3>\n  <p>“Azure VM Scale Set manages multiple identical VMs automatically.</p>\n  <p>Features:</p>\n  <p>•\tAuto scaling</p>\n  <p>•\tLoad balancing</p>\n  <p>•\tHigh availability</p>\n  <p>Scaling based on:</p>\n  <p>•\tCPU</p>\n  <p>•\tMemory</p>\n  <p>•\tCustom metrics</p>\n  <p>Best for:</p>\n  <p>•\tWeb applications</p>\n  <p>•\tLarge workloads</p>\n  <p>One-line Answer:</p>\n  <p>Scale Set automatically scales and manages multiple VM instances.”</p>\n</div>",
