    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>☁️ <strong>What is Azure Functions?</strong></h3>\n  <p>“Azure Functions is a serverless compute service.</p>\n  <p>Features:</p>\n  <p>•\tEvent-driven execution</p>\n  <p>•\tPay-per-use</p>\n  <p>•\tNo server management</p>\n  <p>Triggers:</p>\n  <p>•\tHTTP</p>\n  <p>•\tTimer</p>\n  <p>•\tBlob storage</p>\n  <p>•\tQueue messages</p>\n  <p>One-line Answer:</p>\n  <p>Azure Functions executes code without managing servers.”</p>\n</div>",
