    "category": "CI/CD & Pipelines",
    "question": "What is Jenkins Pipeline?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>What is Jenkins Pipeline?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Jenkins pipeline automates:</p>\n  <p>•\tBuild</p>\n  <p>•\tTest</p>\n  <p>•\tDeployment</p>\n  <p>•\tCI/CD process</p>\n  <p>Flow</p>\n  <p>Code → Build → Test → Deploy</p>\n  <p>Benefits</p>\n  <p>•\tAutomation</p>\n  <p>•\tFaster deployment</p>\n  <p>•\tReduced manual work</p>\n  <p>•\tContinuous Integration</p>\n  <p>Example</p>\n  <p>pipeline {</p>\n  <p>agent any</p>\n  <p>stages {</p>\n  <p>stage('Build') {</p>\n  <p>steps {</p>\n  <p>echo 'Building'</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>stage('Deploy') {</p>\n  <p>steps {</p>\n  <p>echo 'Deploying'</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>Docker Questions</p>\n</div>",
