    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>Data source kya hota hai?</strong></h3>\n  <p>A:</p>\n  <p>Data source se existing infra (jaise existing VPC ID) read-only mode me access karte hain:</p>\n  <p>hcl</p>\n  <p>Copy</p>\n  <p>Edit</p>\n  <p>data \"aws_vpc\" \"existing\" {</p>\n  <p>filter {</p>\n  <p>name = \"tag:Name\"</p>\n  <p>values = [\"prod-vpc\"]</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>}</p>\n  <p>🧠 Real-world and Troubleshooting</p>\n</div>",
