    "question": "CI/CD me Terraform ko kaise use karte hain?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>🏗️ <strong>CI/CD me Terraform ko kaise use karte hain?</strong></h3>\n  <p>A:</p>\n  <p>Use terraform plan in pull request</p>\n  <p>terraform apply in merge step (manual approval)</p>\n  <p>Remote backend + workspace for multi-env (dev/stage/prod)</p>\n  <p>Terraform ke question bhej rehe hu vo prepare karo</p>\n  <p>Output block in terraform</p>\n  <p>Dyanamic block in terrafrom</p>\n  <p>Loops in terraform</p>\n  <p>Count vs for-each ( use case )</p>\n  <p>Validation block</p>\n  <p>Module in terraform</p>\n  <p>Validation block in terrafrom</p>\n  <p>Variables in terraform</p>\n  <p>All 4 file (main,var,tfvars,provider)</p>\n</div>",
