    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>What is taint? Why is it used?</strong></h3>\n  <p>A taint in Kubernetes prevents Pods from being scheduled on a Node unless the Pod tolerates that taint. It ensures that only specific Pods run on specific Nodes.</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li>--</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
