    "question": "What is ESC Tools ?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>What is ESC Tools ?</strong></h3>\n  <p>ESC (Enterprise Security and Compliance) tools secure container pipelines:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Pipeline Scanning</strong>: Scanning container images in ACR for security vulnerabilities before they are deployed.</li>\n    <li><strong>Runtime Security</strong>: Deploying security tools (like Falco, Prisma Cloud, or Defender for Cloud) that monitor container system calls and block abnormal behavior, such as run-time shell executions.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
