    "question": "What is AKS patch management ?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>☸️ <strong>What is AKS patch management ?</strong></h3>\n  <p>AKS node patch management and OS updates:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>OS Updates</strong>: Microsoft automatically downloads security patches to worker nodes daily.</li>\n    <li><strong>Reboot Coordination</strong>: For patches requiring a restart, deploy <strong>Kured</strong> (Kubernetes Reboot Daemon) inside the cluster. Kured sequentially cordons and drains workloads off nodes, triggers OS reboots, and returns them to service, preventing downtime.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
