    "question": "What are the troubleshooting steps ?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>What are the troubleshooting steps ?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Standard troubleshooting steps for DevOps environments:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Isolate layer</strong>: Determine if the failure is infrastructure, network, database, application code, or CI/CD config.</li>\n    <li><strong>Logs check</strong>: Review container console logs (<code>kubectl logs</code>), application stack traces, or pipeline step output logs.</li>\n    <li><strong>Resource health</strong>: Check CPU/Memory capacity bottlenecks, and run port connection tests (curl, telnet, netcat).</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
