    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>☸️ <strong>Creating the cluster ?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Creating a Kubernetes cluster in Azure (AKS) or AWS (EKS):</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Provision Control Plane</strong>: Deploy cluster resources using Terraform (e.g. <code>azurerm_kubernetes_cluster</code>) or CLI commands, configuring networking, node sizes, and auth.</li>\n    <li><strong>Node Pools</strong>: Attach System Node Pools (for control workloads) and User Node Pools (for application containers) running inside designated private subnets.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
