    "question": "What is application Gateway?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>What is application Gateway?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Azure Application Gateway is a Layer 7 regional web load balancer:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Key Capabilities</strong>: Supports SSL Offloading/Termination, URL path-based routing (e.g., routing <code>/images</code> to one backend pool and <code>/api</code> to another), and cookie-based session affinity.</li>\n    <li><strong>Security</strong>: Features integrated Web Application Firewall (WAF) to block SQL injections, cross-site scripting, and OWASP Top 10 vulnerabilities.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
