    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>🐳 <strong>Q. How you call multiple images from docker</strong></h3>\n  <p>Handling multiple images in Docker architectures:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Multi-Stage Builds</strong>: Reference multiple <code>FROM</code> images in a single <code>Dockerfile</code> (e.g. build app in SDK image, copy binary to minimal runtime JRE image). This keeps output container sizes small.</li>\n    <li><strong>Docker Compose</strong>: Define multiple containers/services running from separate images in a single YAML file to deploy them together.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
