    "question": "How have you setup monitoring for VMs?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>How have you setup monitoring for VMs?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Setting up VM monitoring in Azure:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Azure Monitor Agent (AMA)</strong>: Deploy the agent on virtual machines.</li>\n    <li><strong>Data Collection Rules (DCR)</strong>: Define DCRs to stream syslog, event logs, and memory performance metrics.</li>\n    <li><strong>Log Analytics</strong>: Send metrics to Log Analytics, and configure dashboard queries.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
