    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>🏗️ <strong>What is terraform dynamic block and how you use that in code?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Terraform is an open-source Infrastructure as Code (IaC) tool developed by HashiCorp:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Declarative</strong>: Allows DevOps engineers to define cloud resources (networks, VMs, databases, containers) using a high-level configuration language (HCL).</li>\n    <li><strong>Execution State</strong>: Generates execution plans (<code>terraform plan</code>), provisions resource states, and tracks changes in a state file (<code>terraform.tfstate</code>) to manage drift.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
