    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>🏗️ <strong>How to bring state file from remote to local system, explain procedure?</strong></h3>\n  <p>To pull a remote state file to your local system:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li>Run <code>terraform state pull > local_state.tfstate</code>.</li>\n    <li>This downloads a read-only copy of the remote state database to your local machine, allowing safe offline debugging.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
