    "question": "Which scripting language you are comfortable?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💻 <strong>Which scripting language you are comfortable?</strong></h3>\n  <p>For DevOps engineering and systems administration, I am comfortable with:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Bash Scripting</strong>: Used on Linux environments to automate VM setups, process text (awk/sed), write backup scripts, and manage container deployments.</li>\n    <li><strong>Python</strong>: Used for cloud SDK programming, custom alert webhooks, data transformations, and complex system integrations.</li>\n    <li><strong>PowerShell</strong>: Used for managing Windows server configurations, Active Directory commands, and Azure RM scripts.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
