    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💻 <strong>Difference between Self hosted agent and microsoft hosted agent?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Microsoft-hosted vs Self-hosted agents in Azure DevOps:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Microsoft-hosted</strong>: Managed by Microsoft. Clean VM per job, pre-installed software, automatically updated, but has compute limitations and cannot access private networks.</li>\n    <li><strong>Self-hosted</strong>: Configured on your own VMs inside private VNETs. Fast caching, customizable software, but requires OS updates and patching by the DevOps team.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
