    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>How to create a HA for Tomcat bassed server?</strong></h3>\n  <p>To configure High Availability (HA) for a Tomcat application server:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Clustering</strong>: Set up multiple Tomcat server instances across availability zones.</li>\n    <li><strong>Session Replication</strong>: Enable session sharing using Redis cache or Tomcat multicast clustering.</li>\n    <li><strong>Load Balancing</strong>: Place a Layer 7 load balancer (Application Gateway/Nginx) in front of the Tomcat cluster to perform health checks and route traffic.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
