    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>1- what's your current profile and day to day activities?</strong></h3>\n  <p>DevOps Engineer profile and daily activities:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Infrastructure</strong>: Provisioning VNETs, subnets, AKS, storage, and SQL resources using Terraform.</li>\n    <li><strong>Pipelines</strong>: Creating and maintaining YAML CI/CD pipelines in Azure DevOps, configuring variable groups, and troubleshooting build failures.</li>\n    <li><strong>Monitoring</strong>: Reviewing Prometheus alerts, updating Grafana dashboards, and inspecting VM metric utilization.</li>\n    <li><strong>Security</strong>: Rotating Key Vault secrets and running SAST compliance scans.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
