    "question": "2- started with GCP IAM?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>2- started with GCP IAM?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Google Cloud Platform IAM (Identity and Access Management) access control controls:</p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:1.2rem;\">\n    <li><strong>Structure</strong>: Grants access permissions based on WHO (users, Google groups, service accounts) has WHAT role (Viewer, Editor, Owner, or custom roles) on WHICH GCP resource (projects, buckets, VMs).</li>\n    <li><strong>Best Practice</strong>: Follow the principle of least privilege, use service accounts for VM-to-API auth, and assign roles to Groups rather than individual user accounts.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
