    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>💡 <strong>Have you worked on grafanaand Prometheus?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Here is a breakdown of the key concepts:</p>\n  <p>• Prometheus is an open-source monitoring tool that scrapes metrics from target endpoints, stores time-series data, and triggers alerts via Alertmanager.</p>\n  <p>• Grafana is an open-source visualization dashboard that connects to time-series databases like Prometheus or Azure Monitor to display real-time metrics.</p>\n</div>",
