    "question": "What is Kubernetes and explain the different services in Kubernetes. 1-How many types of declare & store the variable in Terraform?",
    "answer": "<div class=\"answer-rich\">\n  <h3>🏗️ <strong>What is Kubernetes and explain the different services in Kubernetes. 1-How many types of declare & store the variable in Terraform?</strong></h3>\n  <p>Types: string, number, bool, list, map, object, tuple.</p>\n  <p>Declaration: In variables.tf file using variable block.</p>\n  <p>Storage: Values can be passed via default value, terraform.tfvars, CLI using -var, or environment variables.</p>\n</div>",
