    "category": "Docker & Kubernetes",
    "question": "What is the smallest component in AKS?",
    "answer": "<div class='answer-rich'>\n      < p > <strong>Pod < /strong> is the smallest deployable component in AKS — it runs one or more containers with shared network and storage context.</p >\n      </div>",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
